{"tid":2347605,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：提醒市民限聚令及口罩令仍然生效 除夕外出消費時請注意人數上限","createTime":"2020-12-31T07:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T15:36:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f153a94ff7f8b9ecd0eb430985153ea3ddddecf1","tid":2347605,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:27:05.000Z","msg":"康文署呼籲市民在除夕晚上切勿聚集及亂拋垃圾<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值廣播員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請在適當時候播出以下報告：<br />\n<br />\n  康樂及文化事務署提醒市民今日（十二月三十一日）除夕晚上到該署轄下場地時，必須保持適當的社交距離，並遵守限制群組聚集的相關法例，以及身處公眾地方時須一直佩戴口罩，違例者可被檢控。<br />\n<br />\n  另外，市民請保持地方清潔，愛護公物，將垃圾放置在垃圾箱內；亂拋垃圾人士會被定額罰款1,500元。<br />\n<br />\n  香港文化中心廣場、梳士巴利花園及尖沙咀海旁會實施人群管制，並會加派人員巡邏，呼籲在場人士遵守有關禁止於公眾地方進行多於法例指定人數的群組聚集及佩戴口罩的規例，以及保持地方清潔。如發現違規情況，會採取執法行動。前往該處的市民請遵守現場工作人員的指示，注意安全。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年12月31日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間15時00分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/31/P2020122400239.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202012%2F31%2FP2020122400239.htm&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm4pVoCVS%2BR9CeaLj%2Fs3YFXo%3D&h=475f8ece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202012/31/P2020122400239.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a7aa715a744a725e0f2097e570449ff99422966e","tid":2347605,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:06:55.000Z","msg":"［壹週刊］阿叻 陳百祥 公然違法 12人黑夜小島飯局4粒鐘無罩豪飲豪食<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2347170\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2347170</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e898a27f268858eb46d7f8b790e916fdb7b2fefa","tid":2347605,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJN04Z5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJN04Z5.jpg&h=7f309b13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a01c4b78995caa42aecfc4835ed7d2a3aebea31d","tid":2347605,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"快cut單程證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}